WEBVTT

00:00.044 --> 00:02.537
<i>Previously on "Better Call Saul..."</i>

00:02.787 --> 00:05.244
I can't believe Davis & Main went for it.

00:05.321 --> 00:06.654
Did you actually think that was gonna fly?

00:06.756 --> 00:07.873
- You can't...
- Tomorrow morning,

00:07.874 --> 00:08.990
eight o'clock, my office,

00:09.092 --> 00:11.526
with the partners,
and we wanna see this thing.

00:11.628 --> 00:13.761
There may have been some solicitation.

00:13.863 --> 00:15.630
I put myself on the line
to get you this job.

00:15.732 --> 00:17.331
So what, you threw me a bone?

00:17.434 --> 00:19.400
It's my word. It's my judgement.

00:19.502 --> 00:22.170
You want next level pay,
you gotta do next level work.

00:22.272 --> 00:23.738
You wanna tell me what we're doing here?

00:23.840 --> 00:26.073
There's a guy.

00:26.176 --> 00:31.045
I need him to go away.

00:31.580 --> 00:33.448
[Door creaks]

00:33.483 --> 00:36.784
[Dog barking in distance]

00:38.395 --> 00:40.428
[Door creaks]

00:42.432 --> 00:44.899
